Final Determination

The decentralisation of intelligence is not an unfortunate side effect of AI success. It is the mature expression of that success.

Accordingly, the long-run destiny of the truly successful AI company is not infinite centrality.

It is historical absorption.

It builds the roads.
The world learns to travel.
Rome remains important.
But it is no longer the only place that knows where the roads go.
